<p>Yeah, so---</p><p>Hi Folks,</p><p>It has been my experience also that an unsolicitated recommendation or endorsement of the looking is usually met by a blank stare or cocked head that, if verbalized, would probably be something like this:  "Pardon me, you've mistaken me for someone who cares!"  But, we certainly have each other and these wonderfully honest shared experiences, and that, to me, is more than sufficient!</p><p>In Love and Peace,</p><p>Don</p>
